'''Mexico''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the capital, Mexico City, along with Cabo San Lucas, Cancun, Guadalajara, Juarez, Mazatlan, Monterrey, Nogales, Puerto Vallarta, and Tijuana.
